toppr
-----

toppr is a Perl program that retrieves last.fm statistics and auto posts them 
to a Movable Type blog.  It's essentially a blog version of what tweekly.fm 
does for Twitter.

Installation
------------

Copy toppr to a directory of your choice.

You'll need the following modules from the CPAN:

Net::LastFM
WWW::Mechanize

Usage
-----

./toppr

Configuration
-------------

You'll need a last.fm api_key and api_secret freely obtainable here:

http://www.last.fm/api/account
